      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This vehicle is looking for a new home with someone who isn't afraid to roll up their sleeves. While it currently needs significant mechanical and cosmetic work, it offers a great foundation for a restoration project or a valuable source of parts. If you're looking for an affordable way to get your hands on a fixer-upper with potential, this is the one for you!",
