    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade masterpiece in absolute mint condition. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen inclement weather. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like luster protected by a professional ceramic coating; you will find no rock chips, swirls, or imperfections here. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule, featuring taut, unblemished leather, pristine trim, and the original factory scent. Every mechanical system and electronic feature functions with the precision of a new car, supported by a comprehensive, documented service history performed exclusively by authorized technicians. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a showroom-quality example that satisfies the most discerning enthusiast. Complete with all original manuals, two master keys, and a clean history report.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
